  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="grid-12">
      <h2>Grid width overrides</h2>
      <p>If you would like your grid layout to be different on tablet or mobile then you can use these modifier classes to achive just that.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row demo">
    <div class="grid-12 grid-6-mobile"><span>12 Desktop / 6 Mobile</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row demo">
    <div class="grid-12 grid-6-tablet"><span>12 Desktop / 6 Tablet</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row demo">
    <div class="grid-6 grid-12-tablet"><span>6 Desktop / 12 Tablet</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="grid-12">
      <pre><code>&lt;div class="row"&gt;
  &lt;div class="grid-12"&gt;
    ...
    &lt;div class="row"&gt;
      &lt;div class="grid-12 grid-6-mobile"&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="row"&gt;
      &lt;div class="grid-6 grid-12-mobile"&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
